iginating in an AGB\nstar undergoing extramixing. This occurrence may indicate that the extramixing\nprocess is hampered at high metallicity or, equivalently, favored at low\nmetallicity. Similar to O-rich grains no star in our sample shows evidence of\nHBB, expected for massive AGB stars.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 27 Jun 2016 20:30:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-07-06"}
